items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 105 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 22!

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 95 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 20!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 185 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 38.
